No AI Training or Model Improvement Use

The contents of this repository, including source code, documentation,
configuration files, examples, tests, and any other materials, may not be
used to train, fine-tune, evaluate, benchmark, or otherwise improve machine
learning or artificial intelligence models without prior written permission
from the repository owner(s).

This restriction also applies to:

- creating datasets derived from this repository for model training or evaluation
- using repository contents in retrieval pipelines for model development
- using repository contents to improve coding assistants, copilots, or similar systems

If you want to request permission for such use, contact the repository
owner(s) directly.
